## Non-Negotiables

- Do NOT substitute components that are not listed in the widget framework spec for the surface being designed.
- Do NOT invent component variants or props not found in the spec or Storybook.
- If a component is marked `🧪` (experimental), note it in the zone breakdown so the team is aware.
- The framework specs in `widget-frameworks/` are the authoritative source of truth. The Storybook is supplementary reference for component details and visual behavior.
